    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those. they're a good start. could you expand more on the national security and rule of law aspects? my students really need to nail the philosophical point that a nation without borders isn't really a sovereign nation. can you help them frame that argument so it sounds authoritative and grounded in legal principle?",
